{"tid":1443583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]D北角po po放左福建佬!!","createTime":"2019-08-11T09:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:11:18.000Z","uid":253438,"like":781,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"683e0ef9cf852862f70658b5df0528e768cf29eb","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩mon住獨媒北角live <br />\n<br />\n1. Check 一個紅衫福建佬無身分證，嗰個人就自己走返入去富臨皇宮酒樓，po po 想追入去，有一個白衫人擋住，然後其他po po 就叫check Id po po 唔好入去。<br />\n<br />\n2. 搜 另一個紅衫福建佬，唔知搜到啲乜嘢，po po 係咁問佢點解又嗰樣嘢，記者都影唔到同睇唔到係乜，但嗰個人就係咁話唔係佢嘅，係人哋塞落佢度。跟住po po又放左。<br />\n<br />\n大家真係玩空城計撚佢地，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為由啱啱情況推斷，<br />\n有咩事，po po同樣放福建人！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">義士唔可以白白犧牲！！</span></span>！"},{"pid":"859123530400871361299764827c926231936057","tid":1443583,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fd221aeaf505f5bb319200e19b2be9f445acd01","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"去第二區"},{"pid":"147bc04171aa3dca3c12c9fe3c84e9ccf31ff834","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6cef6b0858ca0e8861b3bed41eebfd8e4426cd56","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"c94a02577eab2db5f4ec511609432c0dd404dc8a","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d1fa79613b7832b9a1610edc7c87fb463eb4f7a6","tid":1443583,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52860fdb0baad2a443941f4e6b0504a6d611808e","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"56c71fa5a611e5141e90b86e8f058936d6e8ce6e","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c7cb26971569a7c140bcb51c1a5ac411cf00ef7","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"ae7c7dc89b82a19b29b4541c147aee001bd20a94","tid":1443583,"uid":41245,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=97b71f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">49,509</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 17:22）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"ae454845dc74f0e6c9f5733fbc9660077a6436ef","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82916cafe60c9658309858ec12ebb172f58cb1f2","tid":1443583,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"求link"},{"pid":"12a83ea0a82b013c4074d4a24448192f2b7aff39","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"002d5033915814df45a85649610ef7d3adc5a86f","tid":1443583,"uid":290176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fda1b341ee1adfb93ef43f39b029bec07d1bda3","tid":1443583,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"134551c4eb7aa4a246b86f18f933c8593755bb8e","tid":1443583,"uid":55144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"警黑共大合作"},{"pid":"c9d4d64995eb6f8646aa75c5b87d3f739b6ec8e3","tid":1443583,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b9333f0384be2babf340de64e561d7876dc05f","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82916cafe60c9658309858ec12ebb172f58cb1f2","tid":1443583,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"求link"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/2194376234193688?s=1342763596&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=cl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2Fvideos%2F2194376234193688%3Fs%3D1342763596%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dcl&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKsbSs98ObMN