30995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=97b71f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">49,509</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 17:22）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201