信勇武都好醒好理智<br />\n其實隨時醒過理上智過和理非<br />\n但如果有人堅持去  只可講尊重意願不阻撓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b74217ad5698e68612bc8b53d699653778eb3a","tid":1443583,"uid":4243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"完全碌柒 係咁打唔拉得 又比記者影哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67a48956f71806db4ca5534d9c634350a374a8d","tid":1443583,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"福建佬忍唔住手狂郁記者呀，班狗完全唔撚理架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人日程表提醒事項</span><br />\n［快入幫手！］正版香城Online玩家交流區！要你幫忙更新系統！ ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382217</a><br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能 HKmap.live<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a><br />\n［大整合］明天活動依舊多姿多彩，請大家繼續支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440534</a></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">〈 光復香港 時代革命 〉\n一、徹惡法\n二、非暴動\n三、銷控罪\n四、查警暴\n五、真普選\n六、不落實「社會信用評分」\n七、移除「智慧燈柱」\n八、查721警黑合作</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7641868bbde19e1f59ac5a3a4155c13c1ea1284e","tid":1443583,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"134551c4eb7aa4a246b86f18f933c8593755bb8e","tid":1443583,"uid":55144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"警黑共大合作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"白衫打完人都可以放<br />\n呢班更加會"},{"pid":"dac0e58e460550fa7739b8d94f5b9ac834a60eb8","tid":1443583,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea5ccd3e51ec29f6cba86297da601afaa1b37dd","tid":1443583,"uid":11008,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-0